# .dockerignore
# BLUEPRINT: Composer 2 implements from this structure
# PURPOSE: Docker build context exclusions. Reduces image size, prevents secret leakage,
#          and speeds up builds by excluding unnecessary files. Per spec §26.12 item 340.
# SECTIONS:
#   - Development tools: .venv, .mypy_cache, .pytest_cache, __pycache__
#   - Secrets: .env (real env; .env.example is fine to exclude too)
#   - IDE: .idea, .vscode
#   - OS: .DS_Store
#   - Git: .git, .gitignore, .gitattributes
#   - Documentation: docs/ (not needed in image)
#   - Test files: tests/ (not needed in production image)
#   - Queue: queue/ (operational artifact, not app code)
#   - Skills and prompts: not needed in image
#   - Scripts: only if not needed at runtime
# DESIGN DECISIONS:
#   - tests/ is excluded from production image but may be included in CI build stages
#   - docs/ is excluded — if API serves docs, OpenAPI spec is generated at runtime by FastAPI
#   - .env is excluded — secrets come from environment injection at runtime
#   - .git is always excluded — git history not needed in image

.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.dockerignore

# Development environment
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Secrets — NEVER in image
.env
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
secrets/

# IDE and OS
.idea/
.vscode/
.DS_Store
*.swp

# Python caches
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# Documentation (not needed in image)
docs/
*.md
!apps/api/README.md

# Queue (operational, not app code)
queue/

# Skills, prompts, specs (not app code)
skills/
prompts/
spec/

# Test files (excluded from production image)
**/tests/
**/test_*.py
**/*_test.py

# Node (for optional profiles not included in API image)
node_modules/
apps/web/
apps/mobile/

# Deployment artifacts
deploy/

# Monitoring
monitoring/

# CI/GitHub
.github/

# Scripts (not needed unless used at container entrypoint)
scripts/

# Build outputs
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/
